CDA / Docker + Php Objet + Light Framework.
By Kapweb.

Create an .env file in root folder that contain (example) : 
MARIA_DB_ROOT_PWD=cdaweb
MARIA_DB_USER_PWD=cdaweb

Create an .env file in Project folder that contain (example) : 
DB_HOST=mariadb
DB_PORT=3006
DB_NAME=cdaweb
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=cdaweb

To start the framework : 
- docker compose up -d
- docker exec -it docker_php /bin/sh
- composer install

Go to http://127.0.0.1:8000
Have fun.